{
  "_comment": "The current CHAMPION architecture — the live baseline every new experiment is measured against and stacked on top of. The daemon updates this automatically on each new record; new experiments subclass `config_class` and are judged vs `val` (no baseline re-measure). Empty `stub` => fall back to the bare base config.",
