  "_flags_note": "The champion's defining levers ON TOP OF config_class. The live champion is config_class + these flags; config_class alone is NOT the champion. confirm_paired.py applies these to BOTH arms so the control is the real champion (not the bare base) — prevents the 267 over-credit bug where poly-alibi was confirmed vs plain alibi instead of vs alibi+deepnet.",
  "val": 6.2209,
  "val_note": "PROMOTED 2026-06-16 via 3-seed paired CONFIRM (confirm_paired.py). Trt 3-seed mean (42/123/7 = 6.2125/6.2306/6.2197, std 0.0074) vs ctrl (alibi) 3-seed mean 6.2539, paired Δ-0.0330±0.0098 SEM, well past 0.018 band. Tiny1M3MAlibiConfig + use_deepnet_alpha + use_poly_alibi. Replaces 253-deepnet-alpha (val 6.2367). Alibi + DeepNet-α (Wang 2022, arXiv:2203.00555, α=1/√24, 0 new params) + use_poly_alibi (per-head linear+quadratic distance decay, +48 params, c_h=0 at init). Three different orthogonal axes (positional bias + residual scaling + curvature) compounding at 0.94M/92 steps. See autoresearch/ideas/267-deepnet-poly-alibi/ and autoresearch/closed.md.",
